{"tid":779608,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Hotels.com訂房變住無牌旅館","createTime":"2018-08-14T13:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T14:01:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6446e4d47f1b6612db764cfcdd484f2055004a06","tid":779608,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:55:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180814/20475953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F20475953&d=wq9jQvku7NJ4KL6GfLQC3fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=1c792ae7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F20475953&h=386caffb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180814/20475953</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月14日 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHotels.com&d=wq9jQvku7NJ4KL6GfLQC3fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=5aa9f1b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Hotels.com</a>訂房變住無牌旅館<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180814/large/a0304a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180814%2Flarge%2Fa0304a.gif&h=d8731147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■網站一度抽起涉事旅館，不久疑似同一旅店改名「Art Inn」再上架。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】不少人會使用網上平台預訂酒店，但小心隨時訂到非法旅館。有讀者投訴，<a href=\"http://早前透過Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%97%A9%E5%89%8D%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8EHotels.com&d=wq9jQvku7NJ4KL6GfLQC3fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=b159d587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">早前透過Hotels.com</a>預訂台北旅館，入住時發現店面無合法旅館業標貼，回港後向台北市政府查詢，證實為非法旅館，認為訂房平台莫視消費者權益，更擔心一旦出事旅遊保險不保。《蘋果》隨意抽查訂房平台的台北住宿，發現多間疑似無牌酒店/旅館，部份裝修美輪美奐，每晚收費近千港元。<br />\n<br />\n讀者胡先生上月到台北旅遊，<a href=\"http://透過Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8EHotels.com&d=wq9jQvku7NJ4KL6GfLQC3fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=34a8b158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">透過Hotels.com</a>預訂位於西門町的旅館「藝宿文旅」，三晚房價近500港元。他指，收到預訂收據時已覺奇怪，因訂房平台顯示旅館名為「藝宿文旅」，收據卻寫「藝墅青旅」，但見地址相同加上之前使用平台預訂房間順利，決定依時入住。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事主僅獲賠$100<br />\n<br />\n他形容旅館屬整幢式經營，設前台接待處，但門口或櫃台均無展示黃色旅館業登記證標貼，員工亦未有制服，僅穿普通T恤牛仔褲，難分辨屬旅客或職員。他回港後向台北市政府查詢，獲確認「藝宿文旅」為無牌旅館，<a href=\"http://遂向Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%81%82%E5%90%91Hotels.com&d=wq9jQvku7NJ4KL6GfLQC3fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=692ad50a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">遂向Hotels.com</a>投訴，卻被以100元退款打發。胡先生認為如此大型訂房平台，公然列出非法住宿，擔心一旦有地震等事故，旅遊保險會不保。<br />\n<br />\n台北市政府觀光傳播局資顯示，「藝宿文旅」早於去年9月因未取得旅館業登記證即營業，被罰款30萬元新台幣（約7.8萬港元）；<a href=\"http://但除了Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BD%86%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86Hotels.com&d=wq9jQvku7NJ4KL6GfLQC3fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=59daa57d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">但除了Hotels.com</a>，<a href=\"http://該旅館於其他平台如Booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A9%B2%E6%97%85%E9%A4%A8%E6%96%BC%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%A6%82Booking.com&d=wq9jQvku7NJ4KL6GfLQC3fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=16d95bc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">該旅館於其他平台如Booking.com</a>、永安旅遊網亦能預訂。<a href=\"http://投訴人向Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%91Hotels.com&d=wq9jQvku7NJ4KL6GfLQC3fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=5f4533dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">投訴人向Hotels.com</a>反映後，涉事旅館一度未能訂房，但不久後疑似同一旅店改名「Art Inn」再上架。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣觀光局官方旅宿網<br />\n（<a href=\"https://taiwanstay.net.tw/Home）可查詢台灣酒店/旅館是否合法。《蘋果》在各訂房平台搜尋，再發現多間疑似無牌酒店/旅館，包括薆悅酒店旗下的薆悅精品及大安會館，兩間均為精品酒店，部份房型索價逾千港元；其餘整幢式還有門草行旅、松河璞旅、旅莊等。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftaiwanstay.net.tw%2FHome%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%AF%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%2F%E6%97%85%E9%A4%A8%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%E3%80%8A%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E3%80%8B%E5%9C%A8%E5%90%84%E8%A8%82%E6%88%BF%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E6%90%9C%E5%B0%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%8D%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%93%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E7%84%A1%E7%89%8C%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%2F%E6%97%85%E9%A4%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E8%96%86%E6%82%85%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%96%86%E6%82%85%E7%B2%BE%E5%93%81%E5%8F%8A%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%89%E6%9C%83%E9%A4%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%A9%E9%96%93%E5%9D%87%E7%82%BA%E7%B2%BE%E5%93%81%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%EF%BC%8C%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%BD%E6%88%BF%E5%9E%8B%E7%B4%A2%E5%83%B9%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%EF%BC%9B%E5%85%B6%E9%A4%98%E6%95%B4%E5%B9%A2%E5%BC%8F%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E9%96%80%E8%8D%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%97%85%E3%80%81%E6%9D%BE%E6%B2%B3%E7%92%9E%E6%97%85%E3%80%81%E6%97%85%E8%8E%8A%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82&d=wq9jQvku7NJ4KL6GfLQC3fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=6ddc10d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://taiwanstay.net.tw/Home）可查詢台灣酒店/旅館是否合法。《蘋果》在各訂房平台搜尋，再發現多間疑似無牌酒店/旅館，包括薆悅酒店旗下的薆悅精品及大安會館，兩間均為精品酒店，部份房型索價逾千港元；其餘整幢式還有門草行旅、松河璞旅、旅莊等。</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣觀光局指，未領取旅館業登記證便營業屬違法，非法旅館裁罰金額由新臺幣10至50萬元，並勒令歇業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHotels.com&d=wq9jQvku7NJ4KL6GfLQC3fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=5aa9f1b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Hotels.com</a>回覆指，致力為旅客提供安全交易平台，但對事件並無進一步說明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://Booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBooking.com&d=wq9jQvku7NJ4KL6GfLQC3fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=677c40a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Booking.com</a>至截稿前未回覆。永安旅遊則指，已即時將有關旅館下架，若發現尚有違法旅館將即時下架，並考慮懲處相關供應商或酒店。<br />\n<br />\n■記者嚴敏慧  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n曾偵破公屋短樁　陳裘大貪案<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n住非法旅館受傷無得賠"},{"pid":"bd76b9f41a871eb73ff530713b906bf37b5f120a","tid":779608,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"邊到有得check有冇牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b010862f12dae7b4aee9e04e7695d1f0bf368898","tid":779608,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd76b9f41a871eb73ff530713b906bf37b5f120a","tid":779608,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"邊到有得check有冇牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T14:01:34.000Z","msg":"台灣觀光局官方旅宿網<br />\n（<a href=\"https://taiwanstay.net.tw/Home\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftaiwanstay.net.tw%2FHome&d=wq9jQvku7NJ4KL6GfLQC3fM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=96371195\" target=\"_blank\">https://taiwanstay.net.tw/Home</a>）可查詢台灣酒店/旅館是否合法。"}]}